we will be reviewing a french movie from&nbsp;
1992, called “The Lover”. In this movie,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.800
we will see how a 15 year old girl falls in&nbsp;
love with a 32 year old chinese businessman.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:16.320
