between them. Next day, on her way to school,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:05.600 --> 00:03:10.720
Jane notices Tony’s car, and realizes that Tony&nbsp;
was there to see her. She goes near to the car,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:10.720 --> 00:03:14.560
and kisses Tony through the window.&nbsp;
Jane then quickly enters the school.

00:03:14.560 --> 00:03:19.600
After her school, Jane starts to look around for&nbsp;
Tony, but she doesn’t find him. Then, one day,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:19.600 --> 00:03:24.640
Tony is at her hostel. Jane gets ready and leaves&nbsp;
with him in his car. They both look at each other&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:29.600
but don’t say a word. Tony takes her to a house,&nbsp;
and tells her that this house was gifted to him by&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:29.600 --> 00:03:34.640
his father. Tony tells her that this house was&nbsp;
used by rich chinese men for their mistresses.

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:37.840
Tony tells Jane that he wants to be&nbsp;
in a physical relationship with her,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:41.920
but he is also afraid that he will fall in&nbsp;
love with her. Getting nervous, Tony says&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:41.920 --> 00:03:46.160
that they should leave. But, Jane insists&nbsp;
that she doesn’t mind being his mistress.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:46.160 --> 00:03:50.320
Then, not knowing about Jane’s real age,&nbsp;
