him that since the death of her father,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:58.480 --> 00:04:02.720
her family has been struggling financially.&nbsp;
Tony asks her if she came with him because&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:06.560
