00:04:09.520 --> 00:04:11.760
Jane seems extremely happy to be there.&nbsp;

00:04:11.760 --> 00:04:15.520
Tony grabs his wallet to pay the bill.&nbsp;
He puts down a few bills of money,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:15.520 --> 00:04:21.040
